data.description: Welcome to this exquisite single-story home nestled in the coveted Dorchester II school district. Boasting an open concept design, this residence features a seamless flow from the dining room to the kitchen and open foyer. Hardwood floors grace the dining, kitchen, and foyer areas, while bathrooms showcase elegant tile, and plush carpeting enhances the remaining rooms. Vaulted ceilings in the dining room, family room, and master bedroom create an airy ambiance. The family room offers a gas fireplace, built-in bookshelves, and an entertainment unit above the fireplace, complemented by French doors leading to the backyard. Indulge in the comfort of the master bedroom, complete with a spacious walk-in closet and a master bath featuring a garden tub and dual sinks.Ceiling fans adorn all bedrooms and the family room, ensuring optimal comfort. Two-inch wood blinds adorn windows throughout, with the exception of the picturesque front picture window.  Step outside to a covered back porch with a patio, surrounded by upgraded landscaping featuring plants and flowers. Enjoy the privacy of the corner lot, enclosed by a wood fence, featuring a pergola in the backyard with a side street entrance and dual entrances from the front yard. A dedicated privacy fence conceals the trash can area.  The practical aspects of this home include a two-car garage with a door opener and shelving, a laundry room with additional shelving, and added gutters on the front and back of the home. Immerse yourself in the charm and functionality of this thoughtfully upgraded residence.
